阴性」。「我拿上报告问医生，他告诉我什么病都没有，不用治疗。」三甲医院的检查结果让张先生很是气愤，「我什么病都没有，光泽医院为什么让我花这么多钱治病呢？」 感染 HPV？「治病」花光积蓄 换院检查，指标却一切正常"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-370929c6af5c0f2a0ce116935301ef4a_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "169 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3945967508"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI59Sj76v6g7I7EAMaCTExMTc2NTc4NSCa0cu5BjAAOOkBQAJyCjM5NDU5Njc1MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1731446409.552385", "card_id": "Q_3729807793", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个人在明白什么道理后，就不焦虑了呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1. 普通人，除了努力别无选择。 比你有钱的人，一定比你更努力；比你努力的人，总有一天会比你有钱。虽然世界不公平，但生活却总能找到平衡。 2. 当你想放弃时，试着对自己说，再坚持一天、一周、一个月、甚至一年。你会发现，坚持下去的结果往往出人意料。 3. 人生的下半场，比拼的是毅力和奋斗。变强的路上固然艰辛，但你必须强大，强大到没有人敢轻视你。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3729807793"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI59Sj76v6g7I7EAMaCTExMTcyMjYzOSDaoMC5BjAAOE9AA3IKMzcyOTgwNzc5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1731446409.552852", "card_id": "Q_3880732661", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苏联早在 1937 年就成为世界第二大工业国了，为何奋斗了五十年，工业年年快速增长，还是没有超越美国?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "体量不比美国小。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_c